rometieron eternidad y se inmolaron en la fugacidad, abraz<span style="font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;">aron utopías y se e<span style="font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;">namoraron del<span style="font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;"> cínico&nbsp;</span> desencanto, imaginaron un futuro ilimitado para terminar arrullados en la com<span style="font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;">odidad de la<span style="font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;"> nostalgia<span style="font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;"> de tiempos irrecuperables.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div><div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;">Han visto parti<span style="font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;">r a casi todos los que los antecedían en la l<span style="font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , sans-serif;">inea suce